data.description: Experience the epitome of modern luxury in this upgraded 3-bedroom home with spectacular views of the Las Vegas Strip and Red Rock Preserve. The primary bedroom and guest bedroom downstairs offers convenience and tranquility, while the four bathrooms provide ample space for your family and guests. Step onto the exquisite luxury vinyl flooring that graces the entire home, exuding elegance and easy maintenance. The loft boasts a stylish wet bar and a powder room for your entertainment needs. Don't miss out on this rare gem that combines comfort and style in a prime location.
